&lt;p&gt;This rare opportunity is ideal for an entrepreneurial candidate, as you will be empowered to “think like an owner” and build materials and processes from the ground up, in collaboration with the VP Legal and business owners.&amp;nbsp; You will serve as a thought partner to the business, helping to build the frameworks, templates and playbooks that allow Flex to build and scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hybrid position with on-site expectations of 3 days per week in one of our offices - New York, San Francisco or Salt Lake City. For candidates outside of those three areas, you may be eligible for our relocation assistance program.&lt;/p&gt;
