&lt;li&gt;Build out and maintain playbooks, policies and frameworks and templates for Flex’s bank, partner and commercial transactions, including clear standards, fallback positions, and escalation paths.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop solutions to scale Flex’s legal capabilities by leveraging training and technology.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with and provide strategic and legal advice to various cross-functional teams, including but not limited to sales, product, finance and partnerships.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help build the foundation of a best-in-class legal team, including our in-house commercial function.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep the department and business apprised of new laws and regulations that could have an impact on the company’s commercial business, both regionally and nationally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Voice your opinion and a drive for continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Close strategic deals by finding pragmatic solutions to any issue you encounter.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adapt to change in a fast paced, dynamic environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
