&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Launch readiness&lt;/strong&gt; -- ensuring CS content, AI workflows, training, QA, and BPO enablement are complete before anything ships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Post-launch feedback loops&lt;/strong&gt; -- synthesizing ticket trends, bot conversations, and in-app signals into actionable product recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI workflow ownership&lt;/strong&gt; -- conversational flow design, escalation logic, and routing rules within your domain&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Incident coordination&lt;/strong&gt; -- leading the CS response for Sev 0/1 incidents from first identification through resolution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
