&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will bring first principles thinking, strong modeling skills, sharp attention to detail, comfort working in fast-paced environments, and the executive presence to communicate effectively with senior stakeholders. This is a hybrid position with on-site expectations of three days per week in our New York headquarters. Candidates outside of the NY/NJ area may be eligible for our relocation assistance program.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
