&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Success here is measured in member and business outcomes: more needs prevented or resolved instantly without a human in the loop, leading to lower cost to serve and stronger retention. You&#39;ll own the data-backed point of view on which problems we prevent, which we solve directly, and which we route for follow-up — and tie each to a number on the company scorecard. You&#39;ll run a fast, rigorous experimentation engine, moving from ideation to full experimentation with discipline, and you&#39;ll act as the decision-maker even when consensus isn&#39;t immediate. You&#39;ll report to the Senior Director of Product, Member Health, and hold the final call on the Self-Service roadmap. You&#39;ll represent your product area directly to our CEO, COO, VP of Customer Support, and GM of Housing — so your work is seen, and owned, at the top of the company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Beyond the product surface itself, you&#39;ll help shape Flex&#39;s broader member health strategy as we build out our AI efforts. You&#39;ll sit closer to the member than anyone at Flex — so the hardest problems in the consumer experience are yours to own, and the retention wins that come from solving them are yours to unlock&lt;/p&gt;
